{
  "chapter": 11,
  "chapter_summary": "第11章\"艺惊敌\"主要讲述了芮玮冒名简召舞与马大成一同前往黑堡参加招亲比武。在黑堡，芮玮遇见了昔日恋人林琼菊，但为了复仇不敢相认。华不利连续击败多名应征者，马大成出手却被击败。芮玮为替马大成出气，以天罗掌三招击败曲无往和华不利师兄弟，技惊四座。林三寒的师叔和合二怪张不笑、颜春富显露身份，原来华不利和曲无往是他们的徒弟。林琼菊认出芮玮，但被林三寒制止。俊俏公子（女扮男装）在旁调侃助威。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_da_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "马大成",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱是来应征的！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_da_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "马大成",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也来应征的吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_da_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "马大成",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱姓马，世居鲁东，草字大成，你这位兄弟既然是来应征的，不妨结伴入堡如何？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兄台可是号称鲁东第一劈山掌，马氏世家之后？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_da_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "马大成",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "劈山掌哪敢称得鲁东第一，不过威势吓人而已。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小弟山西芮玮，欲去堡中了结一事，你我正好同路。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_duo_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "何多生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来者何方英雄？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_da_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "马大成",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下鲁东马氏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_duo_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "何多生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦！哦！原来是马兄，请进！请进！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_duo_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "何多生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阁下何人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也配问我的名姓？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "何兄弟，不要问了，他是天池府简大公子！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "简兄前来敝堡，有何事吗？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_da_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "马大成",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奇怪？黑堡主明明宣告天下英雄前来应征其女之婚事，咱们来这里不为此事，为啥事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "简兄前来敝堡，是为应征的吗？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_da_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "马大成",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然是来应征婚事！你们在这里拦着咱们，难道是黑堡的待客之道？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_wen_kai",
      "speaker_name": "黄温凯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请进！请进！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "速报金陵简召舞、鲁东马大成驾到！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_da_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "马大成",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兄弟，你不是自称山西芮玮，怎么他们老称你是金陵的简召舞呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "马兄只要认定我是山西芮玮，管他们叫什么。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_duo_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "何多生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是我们的堡主林三寒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_san_han",
      "speaker_name": "林三寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "能得简公子、马家少爷前来敝堡，真是篷筚生辉。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_da_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "马大成",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有劳堡主出迎，罪过！罪过！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_san_han",
      "speaker_name": "林三寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "林某何幸能邀得各位英雄来此，敬水酒一杯，聊表谢意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_san_han",
      "speaker_name": "林三寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位来此应征，不免要技斗一番，林某请来两位师叔评判，希各位点到为止，大家一面欣赏一面饮酒，千万不要伤了和气。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_chun_xi",
      "speaker_name": "王春西",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们都是来招亲的，风闻堡主干金姿容绝世，却未见过，今天不妨请出来，让大家见见可好？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_san_han",
      "speaker_name": "林三寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是王少侠相请，自是要让各位一见。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_san_han",
      "speaker_name": "林三寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "菊儿，抬起头来！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_san_han",
      "speaker_name": "林三寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "菊儿，还不抬起头来？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_san_han",
      "speaker_name": "林三寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "菊儿，坐到爹的身边来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_san_han",
      "speaker_name": "林三寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁请先上场？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_bu_li",
      "speaker_name": "华不利",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下华不利，先下场讨教。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_bu_bai",
      "speaker_name": "冯不败",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下华山冯不败，领教阁下拳法。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_bu_li",
      "speaker_name": "华不利",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "冯不败！好可笑的名字！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_bu_bai",
      "speaker_name": "冯不败",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下输了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_bu_li",
      "speaker_name": "华不利",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么！你不是叫冯不败吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_bu_li",
      "speaker_name": "华不利",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪位再来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_san_han",
      "speaker_name": "林三寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王少侠既请出林某的女儿，怎么不下场比个高下，莫非瞧不上我女儿吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_bu_li",
      "speaker_name": "华不利",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下从不使用兵刃，你既用剑，就用剑攻吧，否则显不出你的家传绝学。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_bu_li",
      "speaker_name": "华不利",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下哪想到所谓名家之后，竟是如此差劲，可笑！可笑！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_xia",
      "speaker_name": "少侠们",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下领教！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_bu_li",
      "speaker_name": "华不利",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也好，大家一齐上吧！免得麻烦。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_xia",
      "speaker_name": "少侠们",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下一人打你就够了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_bu_li",
      "speaker_name": "华不利",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既不愿群斗，一个一个等着慢慢来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_bu_li",
      "speaker_name": "华不利",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在座各位敢称天下的英雄前来应征，真是十分可笑之事，看来你们乖乖回去，让我一人得胜算了！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_da_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "马大成",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他奶奶的，谁敢狂？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_bu_li",
      "speaker_name": "华不利",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阁下何人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_da_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "马大成",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱是要真与你打一架，用不着问姓名，败了再说。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_bu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "张不笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鲁东的劈山掌力太狠毒，今日看来，果然非凡？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_san_han",
      "speaker_name": "林三寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师叔说的不错，若是贸然接上一掌定要吃个大亏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_da_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "马大成",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兄弟，咱打败了……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_da_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "马大成",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兄弟，咱没事了，谢谢你……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "马兄不要说话，看我替你出口气。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_bu_li",
      "speaker_name": "华不利",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "简公子也是来招亲的吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小玮！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_san_han",
      "speaker_name": "林三寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "菊儿，怎么啦！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他……他……他……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_san_han",
      "speaker_name": "林三寒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他不是那个姓芮的小子，你紧张什么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_bu_li",
      "speaker_name": "华不利",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你既不是来招亲的，在下不愿与你比斗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不愿动手，就像马大成那样，在胸口上自己捶一拳　吧！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_bu_li",
      "speaker_name": "华不利",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不是疯子，为何要打自己一拳！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你刚才怎么打人，就该怎么打自己，要是再不动手，我可要动手了！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还不自个了断吗？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_wang",
      "speaker_name": "曲无往",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "简公子不要欺人大甚！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_bu_li",
      "speaker_name": "华不利",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师兄，可要小心一点！",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_wu_wang",
      "speaker_name": "曲无往",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你回去，曲无往可不怕天池府中的跳梁小丑！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 376,
